item.title: Whats the Error - Dialogues
item.dc:creator: @Skiire Skiire
item.description:
@Skiire wrote:

You’re placing your code in the wrong area. Orphaned case means that case Id is already used (highly unlikely considering it’s 29,188) or it’s outside of a switch statement… Check all your { and make sure they have a closing }. Just re-read your code and make sure it follows conventions.
